      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON COPY (6) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fifth (30.74) at this track in a Grade 5. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. ASTON AZUL (2) was well supported last time and gave a sight after a fast early split but could manage only the minor money, finishing a one length second (17.93) over 305m at this track. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from six starts. Expecting another good run. ASTON JIMENA (8) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 12 lengths sixth (24.20) last time in a Other at this track over 400m. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from on outside draw. Must include in calculations. COMPTON FRANKY (4) showed great speed to lead all the way last start. Will give a great sight.",
